.Dt GETMAXPARTITIONS 3
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm getmaxpartitions
.Nd get the maximum number of partitions allowed per disk
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.In util.h
.Ft int
.Fn getmaxpartitions void
.Sh DESCRIPTION
.Fn getmaxpartitions
returns the number of partitions that are allowed per disk on the
system.
